Date of Birth: May 6, 1915<br/>
Birthplace: Salt Lake City, Utah, USA<br/>
Ordained apostle: December 2, 1971<br/>
Death: February 25, 1994<br/>
<br/>
Born May 6, 1915, in Salt Lake City, Salt Lake Co., Utah, to Marvin O.
Ashton and Rachel Jeremy. Sustained Assistant to the Twelve Apostles Oct. 3, 1969, at age 54;
ordained apostle on Dec. 2, 1971, by Harold B. Lee at age 56; died Feb. 25, 1994, at Salt Lake City, Salt Lake Co., Utah, at age 78.